SON> Metz </PERSON>, who is baking the dessert for the gala. `` We have a responsibility to lead, and I'm actually somewhat disappointed in the lack of corporate responsibility that I see on the part of some of the fastfood people.'' Education is the main ingredient to healthy eating, and the <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> York </LOCATION> institute's 22,000 graduates are busy `` spreading the word,'' according to <PERSON> Metz </PERSON>. `` The message will get around,'' he said. `` It's an enormous undertaking, but I think we're making progress.''
