ll outstanding stock of <ORGANIZATION> UA </ORGANIZATION>'s parent company, <ORGANIZATION> Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer_United </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Artists </ORGANIZATION>, at $ 20 a share. <ORGANIZATION> Qintex </ORGANIZATION>, best known in the <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION> as one of the makers of the <ORGANIZATION> CBS </ORGANIZATION> miniseries `` Lonesome Dove,'' would get the <ORGANIZATION> UA </ORGANIZATION> moviemaking group and its film library. But <PERSON> Kerkorian </PERSON> would retain control of the <ORGANIZATION> MGM </ORGANIZATION> name and its TV and movie studios, as well as 34 <ORGANIZATION> MGM </ORGANIZATION> movies, including `` Moonstruck'' and `` A Fish Called <PERSON> Wanda </PERSON>.''
